        "# Ratio of probabilities\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "ratio(w_i)=\\frac{P(w_i|+)}{P(w_i|-)} \\approx \\frac{freq(w_i|+)+1}{freq(w_i|-)+1}\n",
