        "\n",
        "taking logs we get\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "  \\log \\frac{P(+|T)}{P(−|T)} = \\log \\frac {P(+)}{P(-)} + \\sum^m_{i=1} \\lambda(w_i) > 0 \n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "where \n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        " \\lambda(w_i) = log \\frac {P(w_i|+)}{P(w_i|−)} \n",
